tDockerfile`：无 Dockerfile → 保存不包含 dockerfile_path\n352: - [ ] 14.5 测试 `TestUpdatePackMetadata_FullMetadata`：所有字段（entrypoint, language, port, build_mode, description）正确保存\n353: \n354: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_metadata_update.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Pack metadata update 场景\n355: \n356: ---\n357: \n358: ## T15. 实现输出路径准备 — PackRuntime._prepare_output_path\n359: \n360: - [ ] 15.1 实现 `_prepare_output_path(self, workspace_path: Path, output_path: Optional[str]) -> Path`：\n361:   - 如 `output_path` 为 None → 返回 `workspace_path`\n362:   - 如 `output_path` 非 None → 创建中间目录（`os.makedirs(output_path, exist_ok=True)`），返回 `Path(output_path).resolve()`\n363: - [ ] 15.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_output.py`\n364: - [ ] 15.3 测试 `TestPrepareOutputPath_Default`：无 `--output` → 返回 workspace_path\n365: - [ ] 15.4 测试 `TestPrepareOutputPath_Custom`：`--output \"/tmp/packed\"` → 返回 `/tmp/packed`，创建目录\n366: - [ ] 15.5 测试 `TestPrepareOutputPath_NestedDirs`：`--output \"/tmp/a/b/c\"` → 创建嵌套目录\n367: \n368: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_output.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Output path preparation 全部场景\n369: \n370: ---\n371: \n372: ## T16. 实现 PackRuntime.pack() 主编排方法\n373: \n374: - [ ] 16.1 实现 `pack(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n375:   - 按顺序调用：\n376:     1. `self._validate_workspace_structure(workspace_path)`\n377:     2. `metadata = self._load_or_create_metadata(workspace_path, options)`\n378:     3. `metadata = self._apply_option_overrides(metadata, options)`\n379:     4. `self._infer_entrypoint` 如 metadata.entrypoint 为 None 则推断并设置\n380:     5. `self._validate_language_compatibility(workspace_path, metadata)`\n381:     6. `self._process_dependencies(workspace_path, metadata)`\n382:     7. `dockerfile_path = self._generate_dockerfile(workspace_path, metadata)`\n383:     8. `self._update_pack_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, dockerfile_path)`\n384:     9. `output_path = self._prepare_output_path(workspace_path, options.get(\"output\"))`\n385:   - 返回 dict：\n386:     ```python\n387:     {\n388:         \"agent_name\": metadata.agent_name,\n389:         \"workspace_path\": str(workspace_path),\n390:         \"metadata_path\": str(workspace_path / \"agent_metadata.yaml\"),\n391:         \"dockerfile_path\": str(dockerfile_path) if dockerfile_path else None,\n392:         \"output_path\": str(output_path),\n393:     }\n394:     ```\n395: - [ ] 16.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_integration.py`\n396: - [ ] 16.3 测试 `TestPack_PythonAgent_FullFlow`：完整 Python agent 工作区 → 成功打包，返回正确结果\n397: - [ ] 16.4 测试 `TestPack_JavaAgent_FullFlow`：完整 Java agent 工作区 → 成功打包\n398: - [ ] 16.5 测试 `TestPack_WithExistingDockerfile`：已有 Dockerfile → 不覆盖\n399: - [ ] 16.6 测试 `TestPack_WithExistingMetadata`：已有 `agent_metadata.yaml` → 加载并合并\n400: - [ ] 16.7 测试 `TestPack_InvalidWorkspace`：无效工作区 → 异常传播\n401: - [ ] 16.8 测试 `TestPack_MissingEntrypoint`：无法推断 entrypoint → `ValueError`\n402: \n403: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_pack_runtime_integration.py -v` 全部通过\n404: \n405: ---\n406: \n407: ## T17. 实现 CLI pack 命令入口 — agentcube/cli/main.py\n408: \n409: - [ ] 17.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n410: - [ ] 17.2 定义 Typer app：\n411:   ```python\n412:   app = typer.Typer(\n413:       name=\"agentcube\",\n414:       help=\"AgentCube CLI - A developer tool for AI agent lifecycle management.\",\n415:       no_args_is_help=True,\n416:       rich_markup_mode=\"rich\",\n417:       add_completion=False,\n418:   )\n419:   ```\n420: - [ ] 17.3 实现 `version_callback` 函数：打印 `agentcube.__version__` 并 `raise typer.Exit()`\n421: - [ ] 17.4 实现 `@app.callback()` root callback：\n422:   - `--version` 选项（eager, callback=version_callback）\n423:   - `--verbose` / `-v` 选项\n424:   - verbose 时调用 `logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)`\n425: - [ ] 17.5 实现 `_handle_error(e: Exception, command_name: str, verbose: bool) -> None`：\n426:   - 打印 `[red]Error {command_name}: {e}[/red]`\n427:   - verbose 时打印 `console.print_exception()`\n428:   - `raise typer.Exit(1)`\n429: - [ ] 17.6 实现 `@app.command()` pack 命令：\n430:   - 选项：`workspace` (`-f`, 默认 `.`), `agent_name`, `language`, `entrypoint`, `port`, `build_mode`, `description`, `output`, `verbose`\n431:   - 使用 Rich `Progress` + `SpinnerColumn` 显示执行进度\n432:   - 调用 `PackRuntime(verbose=verbose).pack(workspace_path, **options)`\n433:   - 成功时 Rich 输出：`agent_name`, `workspace_path`, `metadata_path`\n434:   - 异常时调用 `_handle_error(e, \"packaging agent\", verbose)`\n435: - [ ] 17.7 更新 `agentcube/__init__.py` 导出：`app`, `PackRuntime`, `MetadataOptions`\n436: - [ ] 17.8 更新 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` 重新导出 `PackRuntime` 和 `MetadataOptions`\n437: - [ ] 17.9 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_pack_command.py`\n438: - [ ] 17.10 测试 `TestPackCommand_DefaultOptions`：无选项 → 使用默认 workspace `.`\n439: - [ ] 17.11 测试 `TestPackCommand_CustomWorkspace`：`-f /path/to/workspace` → 使用指定路径\n440: - [ ] 17.12 测试 `TestPackCommand_AllOptions`：传递全部选项 → 正确传递给 PackRuntime\n441: - [ ] 17.13 测试 `TestPackCommand_SuccessOutput`：成功时显示 agent_name, workspace_path, metadata_path\n442: - [ ] 17.14 测试 `TestPackCommand_ErrorNoVerbose`：失败无 verbose → 显示红色错误，无 traceback\n443: - [ ] 17.15 测试 `TestPackCommand_ErrorVerbose`：失败有 verbose → 显示红色错误 + traceback\n444: - [ ] 17.16 测试 `TestPackCommand_ExitCodeOnError`：失败 → exit code 1\n445: - [ ] 17.17 测试 `TestPackCommand_ProgressSpinner`：执行期间显示 Progress spinner\n446: - [ ] 17.18 测试 `TestRootCallback_Version`：`--version` → 打印版本号并退出\n447: - [ ] 17.19 测试 `TestRootCallback_Verbose`：`-v` → 启用 DEBUG logging\n448: - [ ] 17.20 测试 `TestRootCallback_NoArgs`：无子命令 → 显示 help\n449: \n450: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_pack_command.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Pack error handling 全部场景\n451: \n452: ---\n453: \n454: ## T18. 创建示例工作区\n455: \n456: - [ ] 18.1 创建 `cmd/cli/examples/hello-agent/` 目录：\n457:   - `main.py`：简单 Python agent 示例（打印 \"Hello from AgentCube!\"）\n458:   - `requirements.txt`：空或最小依赖\n